<!-- pages/profile/profile.wxml -->
<!-- 职责：个人中心页视图 —— 头像/昵称、统计数据、梦境简要列表、退出登录 -->

<view class="profile-page deep-space-bg">

  <!-- 顶部导航栏占位 -->
  <view class="nav-placeholder"></view>

  <scroll-view scroll-y class="profile-scroll safe-bottom">

    <!-- 用户信息卡 -->
    <view class="user-card glass-card">
      <image
        class="user-avatar"
        src="{{userInfo.avatarUrl || '/assets/icons/default-avatar.png'}}"
        mode="aspectFill"
      />
      <!-- 昵称正常模式 -->
      <view wx:if="{{!isEditingNick}}" class="user-nick-row">
        <text class="user-nick">{{userInfo.nickName || '梦境旅人'}}</text>
        <text class="nick-edit-btn" bindtap="onEditNick">编辑</text>
      </view>
      <!-- 昵称编辑模式 -->
      <view wx:else class="user-nick-edit">
        <input
          class="nick-input"
          value="{{nickNameInput}}"
          bindinput="onNickInput"
          placeholder="请输入昵称"
          placeholder-class="input-placeholder"
          maxlength="20"
          focus
        />
        <view class="nick-actions">
          <text class="nick-cancel" bindtap="onCancelNick">取消</text>
          <text class="nick-save" bindtap="onSaveNick">保存</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 统计面板 -->
    <view class="stats-panel">
      <view class="stat-item glass-card">
        <text class="stat-value">{{stats.totalCount}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">梦境总数</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item glass-card">
        <text class="stat-value">{{stats.monthCount}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">本月记录</text>
      </view>
      <view class="stat-item glass-card">
        <text class="stat-value stat-mood">{{stats.topMood}}</text>
        <text class="stat-label">最常情绪</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 梦境简要列表 -->
    <view class="section-header">
      <text class="section-title">我的梦境</text>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{isLoading}}" class="loading-spinner">
      <text>加载中...</text>
    </view>

    <view wx:elif="{{dreamList.length === 0}}" class="empty-state">
      <text>还没有任何梦境记录</text>
    </view>

    <view wx:else class="dream-list">
      <view
        wx:for="{{dreamList}}"
        wx:key="_id"
        class="dream-list-item glass-card"
        data-id="{{item._id}}"
        bindtap="onDreamTap"
      >
        <view class="dream-list-left">
          <text class="dream-list-title">{{item.title}}</text>
          <text class="dream-list-date">{{item.date}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="dream-list-right">
          <view class="bubble-tag">{{item.moodLabel}}</view>
          <text class="dream-list-arrow">›</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- 退出登录 -->
    <view class="logout-area">
      <button class="logout-btn" bindtap="onLogout">退出登录</button>
    </view>

  </scroll-view>
</view>
